Breckin Meyer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Breckin_Meyer 0 Breckin Erin Meyer (born May 7, 1974) is an American actor, voice actor, writer, producer and drummer known for his roles in films such as Clueless, Road Trip, Rat Race and Garfield: The Movie.
